  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cmain\u003e\u003carticle aria-label=\"Appletini\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAn Appletini (Apple Martini) is made with only four ingredients and is easy to make and certainly far too easy to drink. It’s a dessert martini that leans toward the sweet side. In this post, I’ll share my Appletini recipe along with ways to change it up to suit your taste. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhile I usually make this recipe with vodka, you could swap it for gin for a slightly more floral, and more classic martini variation. You could also choose to add a little cinnamon and sugar to the rim to up the dessert martini vibes.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRelated:\u003c/strong\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/washington-apple-shot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eWashington Apple Shot\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/bees-knees-cocktail/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eBee’s Knees\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/lychee-martini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eLychee Martini\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/easy-at-home-chocolate-martini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eChocolate Martini\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/rum-runner/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eRum Runner\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/easy-espresso-martini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eEspresso Martini\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/vesper-martini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eVesper Martini\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/caramel-apple-martini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eCaramel Apple Martini\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u