ess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-recipe.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-ingredients\"\u003eIngredients \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVodka \u003c/strong\u003e– Choose a quality vodka such as Ketel One, Tito’s or Grey Goose.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eApple Juice\u003c/strong\u003e – The apple flavor in this recipe comes from both apple juice and the schnapps liqueur.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSour Apple Schnapps\u003c/strong\u003e – This is where the sour apple flavor comes in as well as the green color.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLemon Juice\u003c/strong\u003e – Freshly squeezed.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOptional Garnish\u003c/strong\u003e – We like to use a slice of Granny Smith apple as an optional garnish.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou’ll see in the photo below I used a sparkling apple juice for the Appletinis pictured here, but this is not necessary. Any apple juice will work.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/appletini/?tp_image_id=118643\" data-pin-title=\"appletini\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/best-Appletini-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-src