lmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-257x300.jpg 257w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-878x1024.jpg 878w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-768x896.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-86x100.jpg 86w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-51x60.jpg 51w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-750x875.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-730x852.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-700x817.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-550x642.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-156x182.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201400\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-257x300.jpg 257w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-878x1024.jpg 878w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-768x896.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-86x100.jpg 86w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-51x60.jpg 51w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-750x875.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-730x852.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-700x817.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-550x642.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients-156x182.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-ingredients.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-tips-amp-substitutions\"\u003eTips \u0026amp; Substitutions\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou could use gin instead of vodka if you prefer. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eAny kind of apple juice works fine. You could also use an apple cider for this recipe. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eStore clean martini glasses in your freezer and you’ll always have a chilled glass ready for when you need it. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eIf you don’t have a \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3FeBc1f\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow\"\u003ecocktail shaker\u003c/a\u003e, a mason jar with a lid will also work. Simply strain through a \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3RVb96K\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow\"\u003ecocktail strainer\u003c/a\u003e to keep the ice from getting into your chilled drink. \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-history-of-the-appletini\"\u003eHistory of the Appletini \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis drink was created on the Fourth of July in West Hollywood at a bar called Lola’s. The owner, Loren “Lola” Dunsworth, was approached by reps from Ketel One vodka to create a signature martini. She noticed an unused bottle of apple schnapps and asked bartender Adam Karsten to mix up a drink.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn pop culture, the Appletini was the drink Zach Braff’s character ordered on \u003cem\u003eScrubs\u003c/em\u003e. It was also the drink of choice for Mark Zuckerberg and Sean Parker’s meeting in \u003cem\u003eThe Social Network \u003c/em\u003emovie. Why not enjoy a delicious Appletini?\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/appletini/?tp_image_id=118645\" data-pin-title=\"appletini\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Appletini.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-more-apple-recipes-you-ll-love\"\u003eMore Apple Recipes You’ll Love:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/homemade-caramel-apples/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eCaramel Apples\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/candy-apples/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow\"\u003eCandy Apples\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/apple-tart/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eApple Tart\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/apple-cobbler/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eApple Cobbler\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/easy-apple-dumplings/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eApple Dumplings\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/easy-apple-pie-bars/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eApple Pie Bars\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/baked-apple-donuts-with-cinnamon-sugar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eBaked Apple Donuts\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/no-bake-caramel-apple-cheesecake/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eNo Bake Caramel Apple Cheesecake\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/spiced-apple-cider-recipe/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eSpiced Apple Cider\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/caramel-apple-cheesecake/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eCaramel Apple Cheesecake\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch2\u003eFrequently Asked Questions\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1660152942311\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhat is schnapps? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eAn alcoholic drink that can be made from various grains and is usually distilled with some type of flavor like fruit or herbs. While schnapps can be drunk on its own, it’s often an ingredient in cocktails. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1660152944117\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eIs it vodka or gin in a martini?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eA classic martini is made with gin, but you can make a martini with vodka. Many dessert martinis are made with vodka so the other flavors can take center stage. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1660152945459\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhat’s in an Appletini?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eVodka, apple juice, sour apple schnapps and lemon juice. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-118739\" data-recipe-id=\"118739\" data-servings=\"1\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"acf-helper-block_f5ebbbd2f7735e2fcee06614b38dc74a\"\u003e\n\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGet our FREE recipe guide with our \u003cem\u003emost popular\u003c/em\u003e recipes of all time!\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"#popup-1\" data-lity=\"\"\u003eGet the Guide\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003csection\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch3\u003eIngredients\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"118739\" data-servings=\"1\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1 ½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003evodka\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounce\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eapple juice\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounce\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003esour apple schnapps\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounce \u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003elemon juice\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"118739\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cp\u003ecocktail shaker\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \n\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ch3\u003eInstructions\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"118739\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-118739-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIn a cocktail shaker, add all ingredients.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-118739-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAdd ice. Shake vigorously until the outside of the shaker feels very cold against your hand. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-118739-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eStain into a chilled martini glass.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-118739-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGarnish with a Granny Smith apple slice (optional).\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \n\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIf you don’t have a cocktail shaker, you can use a mason jar with a lid and then strain with a cocktail shaker into your martini glass. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\u003cdetails\u003e\n\n    \u003csummary\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cp\u003eNutrition Facts\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAppletini\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAmount per Serving\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e% Daily Value*\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e* Percent Daily Values are based on a 2000 calorie diet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eNotice: Nutrition is auto-calculated, using Spoonacular, for your convenience. Where relevant, we recommend using your own nutrition calculations.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/details\u003e\n\n\n\t\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003c/main\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
